i## 移动 Nix Daemon 的临时文件夹		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i在给软件打包时，Nix Daemon 会将临时文件存在 `/tmp` 目录下。如果 `/tmp`		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i是内存盘，打大型软件包（例如 Linux 内核）时容易爆内存。		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iNixOS 的 `/tmp` 默认不是内存盘，但随着我们的配置，`/tmp` 也将被存放在		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i根目录的内存盘上。因此，我们可以将 Nix Daemon 的临时文件移动到硬盘上，		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i例如我设置的是 `/var/cache/nix`：		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i```nix		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
isystemd.services.nix-daemon = {		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  environment = {		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    # 指定临时文件的位置		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    TMPDIR = "/var/cache/nix";		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  };		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  serviceConfig = {		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    # 在 Nix Daemon 启动时自动创建 /var/cache/nix		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i    CacheDirectory = "nix";		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i  };		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
